Subject: RE: [VB] Panel in Kombi clothing?

>Does anyone know if all split window panel vans have side louvers towards
the top and all others do not have these top louvers?
>
Yes, top side vents = Panel.  You can also check your M-code plate for the
211 model # or other model starting with 21.  21 = Panel.

Upper vents = bench front seat Panel.  Walk-thrus didn't have the vents.
(Special orders not withstanding)

